@startuml
title Online Quiz System State Transition Diagram

initial : User is not logged in

state "User is not registered" as NotRegistered {}
state "User is registered but not logged in" as NotLoggedIn {}
state "Logged In - Teacher" as TeacherLoggedIn {}
state "Logged In - Student" as StudentLoggedIn {}

NotRegistered --> NotLoggedIn : Register
NotLoggedIn --> NotLoggedIn : Login
NotLoggedIn --> TeacherLoggedIn : Login as teacher
NotLoggedIn --> StudentLoggedIn : Login as student

TeacherLoggedIn --> TeacherLoggedIn : Continue as teacher
TeacherLoggedIn --> TeacherLoggedIn : Create new quiz
TeacherLoggedIn --> TeacherLoggedIn : Edit existing quiz
TeacherLoggedIn --> TeacherLoggedIn : Save as draft
TeacherLoggedIn --> TeacherLoggedIn : Post quiz for students
TeacherLoggedIn --> ViewResults : View quiz results

StudentLoggedIn --> StudentLoggedIn : Select quiz
StudentLoggedIn --> AnswerQuiz : Answer selected quiz
AnswerQuiz --> SubmitQuiz : Submit quiz
SubmitQuiz --> ViewResults : View result after submitting

ViewResults : Final state

@enduml
